info.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 23 at 1:04PM PST until February 24 at 4:00PM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 4 AM TO 4 PM PST FRIDAY... * WHAT...Southwest winds 20 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph expected. * WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Beaches, San Luis Obispo County Inland Central Coast, Santa Lucia Mountains, Southern Salinas Valley and San Luis Obispo County Interior Valleys. * WHEN...From 4 AM to 4 PM PST Friday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
